{"id": "art-1961", "label": "Art. 1961", "title": "Art. 1961", "slug": "art-1961", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1641458248\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1958\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1641458248\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 196<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_803794442\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1957\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_803794442\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259; cu asociat unic, acesta va exercita <span\nclass=SpellE>atribu&#355;iile</span> adun&#259;rii generale a <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1108473981\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1956\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1108473981\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Asociatul unic va consemna de îndat&#259;, în scris,\norice decizie adoptat&#259; în conformitate cu alin. (1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1864766596\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1955\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1864766596\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Asociatul unic poate avea calitatea de salariat al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> cu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259; al\nc&#259;rui asociat unic este.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1802129973\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1954\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1802129973\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)[textul din Art. 196^1, alin. (4) din titlul III,\ncapitolul VI a fost abrogat la 17-apr-2009 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art.\n1, punctul 6. din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> 88/2009</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>"}